# Cloudflare Pages — Loop Messenger (messenger.rald.cloud)
#
# BUG FIX: Previous rule proxied /api/* → messenger.rald.cloud/api/* (circular self-reference).
# Fixed: proxies to chat-api.rald.cloud — the Fly.io Node.js API server.
# DNS required: chat-api.rald.cloud  CNAME  loop-messenger-api.fly.dev  (CF Proxied)
#
# CF Pages transparently forwards API requests so the browser talks only to
# messenger.rald.cloud (same-origin — no CORS preflight overhead).
#
/api/*  https://chat-api.rald.cloud/api/:splat  200

# SPA catch-all — serve index.html for all wouter client-side routes.
# Required for deep-links: /chats/:id, /profile, /settings, /auth, etc.
# Must remain last — Cloudflare Pages matches top-to-bottom.
/*  /index.html  200
